reviewText: 4 B+ movies here. Some of each of them is worth watching. Different stories with smart messages well made, nicely filmed. The heavy weight material is carried with some grace.

Interesting film, but the first 3 films were all about Jews. Well done, but I was a bit surprised about the lack of diversity. The 4th film, Malena, was Italian, in Italian and subtitled. I'm still learning a lot about multi-films on one DVD. Miramax productions are usually of good quality with well-known actors.
